==English==

===Noun===
''Flashback''  Plural: ''Flashbacks''


# a period when you remember something instantaneously and vividly for a short amount of time
#:''He stood there for a moment as if he had one of his '''flashbacks''' again''
# A term used in certain media broadcasts to symbolize the use of media from past periods of times
#:''this is the random 80's '''flashback''' on XFM''

